fehd.ADR_EN: GROUND FLOOR (MAJOR PORTION), PAREKH HOUSE, NO. 63 WYNDHAM STREET, CENTRAL, HONG KONG
fehd.ADR_TC: 香港中環雲咸街63號巴力大廈地下(主要部份)

result.adr_address: 63 Wyndham St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Draft Land HK

reviews.text: This place is fantastic. Excellent cocktails, fast and friendly service, and in a popular area for night life. Their cocktails on tap are able to be sampled before committing! Go here now.
Drinks were great but I was prohibited from eating my roller coasters. This really killed the mood for me. Would recommend it but don't try to eat your own chips or you will be scolded
Loved this interesting concept of cocktails on tap. Staff are friendly and explained the different varieties of drinks in detail.
Great pre batched cocktails. The infused taste is better than other live made cocktails

Interesting concept, but I personally prefer the traditional bar tender mixing the cocktail in front of you, as the bar tender can make the cocktail in accordance to your taste buds. Also you would not know when their pre-mixed cocktail were made.
